
# Conventional commits — type(scope): imperative subject (≤72 characters)
# Types: feat | fix | docs | style | refactor | chore | perf | ci
#
# Examples:
#   fix(brand): show full SOAR lockup in header and footer
#   feat(store): align CTA with center product column
#
# After the subject: blank line, then body (what/why, wrap ~72 cols).
# Lines starting with # are removed from the final message.
